description: Demolition of no 3 Broad Green Avenue; alterations to existing City House to include recladding of existing building and use of ground floor for commercial / nursery use and upper floors as residential accommodation; erection of a four/five/six/seven storey building fronting Campbell Road and a three/ four/five/six storey building fronting Broad Green Avenue, providing a total of 36 studio flats, 109 one bedroom flats, 138 two bedroom flats and 36 three bedroom flats; alterations to vehicular accesses and provision of basement parking
